name: Brimstone - Beastmaster Strikeforce SE
description: #HENHalloween Special Edition. Brimstone's rain of terror not only stretches across the galaxy but also into his enemies dreams and turns them into nightmares. He uses demonic encantations to lull his foes into deep sleep to torture them with their greatest fears and once he's finished has the ability to steal their soul with his demonic staff for those that are unable to snap out of the illusion.
